                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">从方法论上跟《自私的基因》有异曲同工之妙。都是从动态的自然的角度去研究标的物。建的模很有趣。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="435715652">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-435715652" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-435715652" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="435715652">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/argus/">蟲</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-09-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">用价格衡量价值地，很想知道，作者是否身体力行自己的理论</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

